{"books":[{"id":"rmrb","name":"人民日报","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"","files":[],"article":{"title":"到工农兵中去接受再教育（对口剧）","authors":["高达祥　王万旗"],"dates":[{"year":1968,"month":9,"day":23}],"is_range_date":false,"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"到工农兵中去接受再教育（对口剧）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高达祥　王万旗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人物：哥俩："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甲：哥哥大学四年级"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乙：弟弟高中毕业生"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甲：春雷震大地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乙：五洲飘红旗。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甲：祖国山河一片红，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"合：万岁！万岁！毛主席！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乙：这是我哥哥，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甲：这是我弟弟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乙：我今年高中刚毕业，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甲：我上大学四年级。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"合：我们亲哥俩，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"现在演个对口剧。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（锣鼓声欢呼声骤起）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乙：锣鼓阵阵敲得急，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"口号声声冲天起，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席发表最新指"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"示，报告哥哥这个好"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"消息。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵！你看我哥哥来啦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哥哥，你今天为啥走"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"得这样急？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甲：吓我一跳，原来是弟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"弟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我正要找你。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乙：干啥？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甲：报告你一个好消息。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乙：我先告诉你，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甲：我先告诉你，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"合：毛主席发表最新指"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"示，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甲："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乙："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（同时）哥哥弟弟我好欢喜！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"合：毛主席说：“从旧学校"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"培养的学生，多数或"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大多数是能够同工农"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"兵结合的，有些人并"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有所发明、创造，不"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"过要在正确路线领导"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"之下，由工农兵给他"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"们以再教育，彻底改"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"变旧思想。这样的知"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"识分子，工农兵是欢"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"迎的。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甲：毛主席的话是指路灯，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乙：字字句句是真理，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甲：这是对我们最大的关"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乙：这是对我们最大的激"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"励。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甲：和工农兵结合道路宽"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又广，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乙：和工农兵结合前途光"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"明无比。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甲：毛主席给咱指方向，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乙：我们要紧跟永不离。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甲：弟弟，我明天就到工"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"厂去，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乙：哥哥，我明天就到边"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"疆去。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甲：你也去？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乙：咋啦，不同意？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甲：同意，我早就同意！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乙：这还差不离。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甲：弟弟，你到边疆带些"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啥东西？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乙：四卷宝书擎在手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甲：金光灿灿照万里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乙：一把铁锨和大镐，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甲：开出一个新天地。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乙：永远和贫下中农结合"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在一起，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"合：接受工农兵的再教"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"育！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甲：弟弟，我想起往事一"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"桩桩，不由得我心头"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怒火起。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乙：哥哥，你想啥？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甲：咱俩都是贫农子弟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乙：是劳动人民把我们养"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"活的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甲：毛泽东思想阳光来哺"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"育，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乙：工农兵送咱上学校学"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"习，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甲：咱们本应为贫下中农"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"服务，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乙：把知识运用到实践中"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"去。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甲：可是万恶的中国赫鲁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"晓夫，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乙：极力推行修正主义教"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"育，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甲：不叫咱们走出校门，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乙：整天关在屋子里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甲：灌输什么孔孟之道，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乙：升官发财的臭道理，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甲：让我们脱离劳动，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乙：脱离实际，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甲：谁要是和工农兵接近，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乙：就说你没出息。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"合：真是岂有此理！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甲：弟弟，咱俩那年探家"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"回农村，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你可还记得起？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乙：那我永远不会忘记，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甲：父亲叫咱俩去间苗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乙：可分不出那是高粱和"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"玉米。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甲：队里叫咱修理锅驼机，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乙：咱俩翻了半天书，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甲：也不知毛病在那里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乙：咱俩急得干瞪眼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甲：父亲气得直叹气，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乙：那时不知啥原因，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"合：原来就是中国赫鲁晓"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夫搞的鬼把戏！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甲：无产阶级文化大革命"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"的风雷连天起，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乙：把中国赫鲁晓夫打翻"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甲：砸烂了旧的教育，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乙：资产阶级知识分子统"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"治学校的现象再也不"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"能继续下去！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甲：工人阶级领导学校，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乙：工人农民掌管教育，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甲：他们思想最干净，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乙：革命最彻底。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甲：他们知识最丰富，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乙：他们无限忠于毛主席！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甲：走和工农兵相结合的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"道路，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乙：接受工农兵的再教育，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甲：这是毛主席指的方向，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乙：这是历史发展的规律。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甲：毛主席说：农村是一"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"个广阔的天地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乙：在那里是可以大有作"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为的。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甲：这是实情话，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乙：这是革命的真理。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甲：革命先烈为了革命，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抛头颅，洒热血，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"前赴后继，死而后已。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乙：他们想的是什么？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"合：是共产主义！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甲：我们就是要把青春献"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"给“公”字，无限忠"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"于毛主席。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乙：胸怀四海浪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"眼观五洲风雷激！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甲：在广阔的天地里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"合：锻炼改造自己！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甲：弟弟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你看，全国人民意气"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风发，夺取文化大革"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"命全面胜利，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铁水奔流钢花放，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"日日月月创奇迹。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乙：哥哥，你看，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"公社的稻菽千重浪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东思想大普及，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"斗私批修凯歌高，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大批判烈火冲天起，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祖国大地春色骄，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"家家户户举红旗。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甲：弟弟，赶快打行李，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"尽快地到工农兵中间"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"去，接受再教育。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乙：哥哥，看！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"合：红日照大地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"光芒无边际，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"工农兵在招手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"热烈欢迎我们到他们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中间去！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甲：弟弟，走！走！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到工厂滚一身油泥，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在劳动中改造自己，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铁锤砸烂旧世界，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"定让五洲飘红旗。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乙：对，走！走！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到边疆去！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向贫下中农学习，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一把镐举起千斤重，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"开出一个新天地！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"合：走！走！走！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沿着毛主席指引的方"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到工农中间去接受再"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"教育，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"迎接无产阶级文化大"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命的全面胜利！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":1,"page_end":1,"alias":""},"tags":[{"name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"name":"革命大批判","type":"主题/事件"},{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}